    	<milestone n="8r" unit="folio" facs="25"/>
        <head>1° Declinacaõ</head>
        <p>Os nomes acabados em <term xml:lang="ta-Taml">ஆ</term> â saõ da 1° declinaçaõ no <expan>g<ex>enitiv</ex>o</expan> do singular acabã em <term xml:lang="ta-Taml">உடைய</term> uthaïa ou em <term xml:lang="ta-Taml">வினுடய</term>  vinuthaïa no <expan>n<ex>ominativ</ex>o</expan> do plural acabaõp em <term xml:lang="ta-Taml">ககள</term> cal . Tambem vaõ por esta declinacaõ os nomes e huã silaba acabados em <term xml:lang="ta-Taml">வ</term> vuana ut <term xml:lang="ta-Taml">பூ</term> pu.rosa. </p>
        <table>
            <row>
                <cell>Sing.</cell>
                <cell>n<hi rend="superscript">õ</hi></cell>
                <cell xml:lang="ta-Taml">இ.ரா.சா.</cell>
                <cell>iracha</cell>
                <cell>Rei</cell>
            </row>
            <row>
                <cell/>
                <cell>g<hi rend="superscript">õ</hi></cell>
                <cell xml:lang="ta-Taml">இ.ரா.சா.வினு.டை.ய</cell>
                <cell>irachavinouthaïa</cell>
                <cell>do Rei</cell>
            </row>
            <row>
                <cell/>
                <cell>d<hi rend="superscript">õ</hi></cell>
                <cell xml:lang="ta-Taml">இ.ரா.சா.வு.ககு</cell>
                <cell>irachavouccou</cell>
                <cell>au, ou, pera o Rei</cell>
            </row>
            <row>
                <cell/><cell>ac<hi rend="superscript">õ</hi></cell><cell xml:lang="ta-Taml">இ.ரா.சா.வை</cell><cell>irachavaï</cell><cell>o Rei, ou, ao Rei, ou, pera o Rei</cell>
            </row>
            <row>
                <cell/><cell>v<hi rend="superscript">õ</hi></cell><cell xml:lang="ta-Taml">இ.ரா.சா.வெ</cell><cell>irachavé</cell><cell>ô Rei</cell>
            </row>
            <row>
                <cell/><cell>ab<hi rend="superscript">õ</hi></cell><cell xml:lang="ta-Taml">இ.ரா.சா.வில</cell><cell>irachavil </cell><cell>de Rei, do Rei, no Rei, em Rei</cell>
            </row>
            <row>
                <cell>plur.</cell><cell>n<hi rend="superscript">õ</hi></cell><cell xml:lang="ta-Taml">இ.ரா.சா.ககள</cell><cell>irachaccal</cell><cell>os Reis</cell>
            </row>
            <row>
                <cell/><cell>g<hi rend="superscript">õ</hi></cell><cell xml:lang="ta-Taml">இ.ரா.சா.க்களு.டை.ய</cell><cell>irachaccaloudaïa </cell><cell>de ou dos Reis</cell>
            </row>
            <row>
                <cell/><cell>d<hi rend="superscript">õ</hi></cell><cell xml:lang="ta-Taml">இ.ரா.சா.க.க.ளு.க.கு</cell><cell>irachaccalouccou</cell><cell>aos, ou pera os Reis</cell>
            </row>
            <row>
                <cell/><cell>ac<hi rend="superscript">õ</hi><note place="foot">In prima istanza scrive iracchacaḷ, poi corretto in -cale, infine con -caḷai. In uso vecchia legatura per la rappresentazione di ḷ+ai.</note></cell><cell xml:lang="ta-Taml">இ.ரா.சா.க.க.ளை</cell><cell>irachaccal</cell><cell>os, ou, aos, ou, pera os Reis</cell>
            </row>
            <row>
                <cell/><cell>v<hi rend="superscript">õ</hi></cell><cell xml:lang="ta-Taml">இ.ரா.சா.க.க.ளெ</cell><cell>irachaccalé</cell><cell>ô Reis</cell>
            </row>
            <row>
                <cell/><cell>ab<hi rend="superscript">õ</hi></cell><cell xml:lang="ta-Taml">இ.ரா.சா.க.க.ளல</cell><cell>irachaccalil </cell><cell>de, dos, em, nos, com Reis</cell>
            </row>
        </table>
        <p>a esta declinacaõ se adacem alguns nomes acabados em <term xml:lang="ta-Taml">உ</term> u de doas silabas e a 1° seia breve, ut <term xml:lang="ta-Taml">அனு</term>, anu, lume dos olhos, <term xml:lang="ta-Taml">உரு</term>, urû, champana, <term xml:lang="ta-Taml">கனு</term>, canu, no de arvore. <term xml:lang="ta-Taml">குரு</term>, curû, sacerdote. <term xml:lang="ta-Taml">நடு</term>, nadû, iustica. Et outros os <expan>q<ex>uaes</ex></expan> tem antes da penultima n, ou m, vaõ pollas amba.</p>
        
        <milestone n="9r" unit="folio" facs="27"/>
        <head>2° Declinacaõ</head>
        <p>os nomes acabados am <term xml:lang="ta-Taml"><del>இ</del>இ</term> ina, ou <term xml:lang="ta-Taml">ஐ</term>, aiana, <term xml:lang="ta-Taml">ய</term>, iana vaõ polla 2° et no <expan>n<ex>ominativ</ex>o</expan> do plurar em <term xml:lang="ta-Taml">கள</term> cal, ut <term xml:lang="ta-Taml">தொ.ப்.பி</term> thoppi.</p>
        <table>
            <row>
                <cell>Sing.</cell>
                <cell>n<hi rend="superscript">õ</hi></cell>
                <cell xml:lang="ta-Taml">தொ.ப.பி</cell>
                <cell>toppi</cell>
                <cell>o chappéo</cell>
            </row>
            <row>
                <cell/>
                <cell>g<hi rend="superscript">õ</hi></cell>
                <cell xml:lang="ta-Taml">தொ.ப.பி.யு.டை.ய</cell>
                <cell>toppïïudaïa</cell>
                <cell></cell>
            </row>
            <row>
                <cell/>
                <cell>d<hi rend="superscript">õ</hi></cell>
                <cell xml:lang="ta-Taml">தொ.ப.பி.க.கு</cell>
                <cell>toppicu</cell>
                <cell></cell>
            </row>
            <row>
                <cell/><cell>ac<hi rend="superscript">õ</hi></cell><cell xml:lang="ta-Taml">தொ.ப.பி.யை</cell><cell>toppiaï	</cell><cell></cell>
            </row>
            <row>
                <cell/><cell>v<hi rend="superscript">õ</hi></cell><cell xml:lang="ta-Taml">தொ.ப.பி.யெ</cell><cell>toppia</cell><cell></cell>
            </row>
            <row>
                <cell/><cell>ab<hi rend="superscript">õ</hi></cell><cell xml:lang="ta-Taml">தொ.ப.பி.யி.லெ</cell><cell>toppilé</cell><cell></cell>
            </row>
            <row>
                <cell>plur.</cell><cell>n<hi rend="superscript">õ</hi></cell><cell xml:lang="ta-Taml">தொ.ப.பி.க.ள</cell><cell>toppigal</cell><cell></cell>
            </row>
            <row>
                <cell/><cell>g<hi rend="superscript">õ</hi></cell><cell xml:lang="ta-Taml">தொ.ப.பி.க.ளு.டை.ய</cell><cell>toppigaludaïa</cell><cell></cell>
            </row>
            <row>
                <cell/><cell>d<hi rend="superscript">õ</hi></cell><cell xml:lang="ta-Taml">தொ.ப.பி.க.ளு.க.கு</cell><cell>toppigalucu</cell><cell></cell>
            </row>
            <row>
                <cell/><cell>ac<hi rend="superscript">õ</hi></cell><cell xml:lang="ta-Taml">தொ.ப.பி.க.<del>ளெ</del><add place="above">ளை</add><note place="foot">In prima istanza scrive toppigaḷe, poi corretto in -gaḷai.</note></cell><cell>irachaccal</cell><cell></cell>
            </row>
            <row>
                <cell/><cell>v<hi rend="superscript">õ</hi></cell><cell xml:lang="ta-Taml">தொ.ப.பி.க.<del>ள</del><del><add place="above">ளை</add></del><add place="below">ளெ</add><note place="foot">In prima istanza scrive toppigaḷ, poi corretto in -gaḷai, infine in -ḷe.</note></cell><cell>toppigalé</cell><cell></cell>
            </row>
            <row>
                <cell/><cell>ab<hi rend="superscript">õ</hi></cell><cell xml:lang="ta-Taml">தொ.ப.பி.க.ளி.ல</cell><cell>toppigalil</cell><cell></cell>
            </row>
        </table>
        <p>de mesmo modo தலை cabeca. <term xml:lang="ta-Taml">நெய</term> manteiga. Os nomes <sic>da</sic> appellativos fomenos fazem no <expan>v<ex>ocativ</ex>o</expan> em <term xml:lang="ta-Taml">அ</term>, a; et tem a significacaõ do plural ut <term xml:lang="ta-Taml">ம.ற.த.தி.ய, உ.ங.க.ளு.க.கு, னா.ண.மி.ல.லை</term>; marattïa ungalucu nanamillaïïo, as Maratis naõ tem vergonha.
<term xml:lang="ta-Taml">சடடை சடடையினுடைய</term> cabaya 	</p>
